## Data Flow Diagram

```
AppianQueueEnv.reset()
    → randomize QueueConfigs (±20% arrival noise)
    → return obs (48-dim float32)

AppianQueueEnv.step(action)
    │
    ├─ ActionSpace.decode(action)      → {queue: delta}
    ├─ ActionSpace.apply(deltas)       → modified QueueConfigs
    ├─ QueueSimulation.run() × 10     → List[SimulationResult]   [Phase 3]
    ├─ RewardShaper.compute()         → (reward, info)
    └─ return (obs, reward, done, info)

PPO (stable-baselines3)
    │
    ├─ Collects n_steps=2048 transitions
    ├─ Computes GAE advantage estimates
    ├─ Updates policy + value network (10 epochs)
    └─ Checkpoints best model

RLInferenceEngine
    ├─ Loads trained PPO model
    ├─ Gets queue states (synthetic / FeatureStore)
    └─ Writes RLRecommendation → FeatureStore (rl:recommendations:latest)
```

