> [!IMPORTANT]
> **Q2 — Action space granularity:** The plan uses `MultiDiscrete([5]×6)` (±2 agents per queue). Should I add larger deltas like ±3 or ±5 for more aggressive reallocation, or keep ±2 as conservative?

